CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 2, 1966, pg. 12A, reads: "Rebound Fight - Schenley's Marv Snowden, who has been selected to play for the Pennsylvania All Stars in the annual Roundball Classics in April, looks on as two Chester players battle for rebound in state championship game.  In the title tilt Snowden was terrific both on offense and defense... Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Schenley High School basketball player #24 Marvin "Marv" Snowden, converging with Chester player under net, during state championship game, Civic Arena
